{"118408":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/118408-FT9bkwTdii7D.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx118408-zZuOINqjBZYn.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx118408-zZuOINqjBZYn.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx118408-zZuOINqjBZYn.jpg"},"description":"This game’s got me obsessed! It’s like it’s taken over my life... wait—HARD MODE ACTIVATED. No-no-no-no-no! It has literally taken me and thrown me into the part of Penelope Eckhart. Love is easy as the heroine, but as the hated villainess, I’m trying very hard not to die… at the hands of my brothers… the prince… a fork… every possible ending is death! This world is stacked against me, but can my wits and insider game knowledge score the affection of these male characters? Or the reset button???\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Psychological","Romance"],"id":118408,"idMal":133641,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/118408","startDate":{"day":1,"month":5,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Death Is The Only Ending For The Villainess ","The Villain's Ending Is Death ","Seule la mort attend la Vilaine","Penelope – Das Böse ist dem Tod geweiht","O Único Destino da Vilã é a Morte","O Único Destino dos Vilões é a Morte","Единственный конец злодейки - смерть","Єдиний фінал лиходіїв – смерть","Kötülerin Kaderi Yok Olmaktır","Kematian adalah Akhir Sang Antagonis","悪役のエンディングは死のみ","反派角色只有死亡結局","恋爱手游的男主都很危险","恶役只有死亡结局","เป็นตัวร้ายก็ต้องตายเท่านั้น","Przeznaczeniem Złoczyńców jest śmierć"],"title":{"english":"Villains Are Destined to Die","native":"악역의 엔딩은 죽음뿐","romaji":"Agyeogui Ending Jugeumppun","userPreferred":"Agyeogui Ending Jugeumppun"},"type":"MANGA"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:47:35.085826+03:00"},"120980":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/120980-7ak3NnHP5f2X.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4506b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx120980-RZ9WLd0o9hyo.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx120980-RZ9WLd0o9hyo.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx120980-RZ9WLd0o9hyo.jpg"},"description":"Nanotechnology meets martial arts at the Mashin Academy. Yeo-Un’s mother may not be one of the High Priest’s six official wives, but his father’s blood still qualifies him for a chance at the position of Minor Priest. Will a mysterious nanomachine injection from a future descendent help Yeo-un in this fierce competition against his powerful half-siblings?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)\n","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Sci-Fi"],"id":120980,"idMal":147863,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/120980","startDate":{"day":10,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Nano Mashin","某天成为魔神","奈米魔神","ナノ魔神","นาโนมาชิน"],"title":{"english":"Nano Machine","native":"나노마신","romaji":"Nano Machine","userPreferred":"Nano Machine"},"type":"MANGA"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T20:29:41.53175+03:00"},"124090":{"value":{"Media":{"id":124090,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/124090","status":"FINISHED","type":"MANGA","format":"MANGA","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/124090-a7jheNA3vF9f.jpg","chapters":113,"synonyms":["はらはら恋々"],"isAdult":true,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","meanScore":76,"description":"Seung-Ho is dating a sweetheart, Min-Ha but he’s getting tired of her childish behavior. After getting a job followed by a long hiatus, he meets an attractive and talented young boss. He starts to struggle in between his boss and her girlfriend.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+)","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"title":{"english":"Young Boss","native":"어린 상사","romaji":"Eorin Sangsa","userPreferred":"Eorin Sangsa"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e4506b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b124090-ALya6arDXJsN.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b124090-ALya6arDXJsN.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b124090-ALya6arDXJsN.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":5,"month":12,"year":2019},"endDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2021}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:34:18.250321+03:00"},"128724":{"value":{"Media":{"id":128724,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/128724","status":"FINISHED","type":"MANGA","format":"MANGA","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/128724-YC8IrGtFZquS.jpg","chapters":101,"synonyms":["Shall we study at Noryangjin?","Noryangjin","Should I Study at Noryangjin?","セクスタディ"],"isAdult":true,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","meanScore":74,"description":"Han-Soo is an aspiring civil servant, preparing for the civil service exam. One day, he runs into his first love, Ji-Yeon, who also is preparing for an exam. She is joining a notorious \"study club\" for hookups.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+, edited)","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"title":{"english":"Studying in NORYANGJIN","native":"노량진에서 스터디 할까?","romaji":"Noryangjineseo Study Halkka?","userPreferred":"Noryangjineseo Study Halkka?"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e4d65d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx128724-FDonr0KeVnbC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx128724-FDonr0KeVnbC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx128724-FDonr0KeVnbC.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":10,"month":4,"year":2020},"endDate":{"day":19,"month":2,"year":2022}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:41:09.223933+03:00"},"131769":{"value":{"Media":{"id":131769,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/131769","status":"FINISHED","type":"MANGA","format":"MANGA","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/131769-yFZ4WVK1hF75.jpg","chapters":216,"synonyms":["Circles","社團學姊"],"isAdult":true,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","meanScore":82,"description":"This college's drama club puts on huge productions. And the audiences they draw rival Broadway. But I don't know if these guys are showing up for the plays. It might be for the big-titted goddesses putting them on...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","genres":["Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"title":{"english":"Drama Queens","native":"동아리","romaji":"Dongari","userPreferred":"Dongari"},"coverImage":{"color":"#f1bbae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx131769-3YLy2cLklJ68.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx131769-3YLy2cLklJ68.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx131769-3YLy2cLklJ68.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":30,"month":11,"year":2020},"endDate":{"day":19,"month":5,"year":2025}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:34:11.207471+03:00"},"132725":{"value":{"Media":{"chapters":11,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg"},"description":"1. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Seed~; Comic ExE 9\u003cbr\u003e\n2. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Bloom~; Comic ExE 10\u003cbr\u003e\n3. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Lily~; Comic ExE 13\u003cbr\u003e\n4. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Iris~; Comic ExE 25\u003cbr\u003e\n5. Takamine-ke no Ichirinsou ~Gypsophila~; Comic ExE 27\u003cbr\u003e\n6. Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou ~Fruits~ (高嶺家の三輪草 〜Fruits〜, The Three Flowers of The Takamine House ~Fruits~)\u003cbr\u003e\n7. Shoka no Makuai de; COMIC Anthurium 2017-07\u003cbr\u003e\n8. Kaiten Eigyouchuu ~Afternoon Tea~; COMIC X-EROS #21\u003cbr\u003e\n9. Tousian e Youkoso!; COMIC X-EROS #17\u003cBR\u003e\n10. Last Summer; COMIC ExE 16\u003cBR\u003e\n10.5 Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou ~ampoule \"0\"~ (高嶺家の三輪草 〜ampoule 『0』〜, The Three Flowers of The Takamine House ~ampoule “0”~)","endDate":{"day":27,"month":2,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":132725,"idMal":142890,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132725","startDate":{"day":27,"month":2,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Takamine-ke no Nirinka","Takamine-ke no Ichirinsou","Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou","Shoka no Makuai de","Kaiten Eigyouchuu","Tousian e Youkoso!","The Three Flowers of The Takamine House","The Anemone of the Takamine House","Between the Bookshelves ","Welcome to Tousian!"],"title":{"native":"Garden","romaji":"Garden","userPreferred":"Garden"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:05:24.855823+03:00"},"136052":{"value":{"Media":{"id":136052,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/136052","status":"FINISHED","type":"MANGA","format":"MANGA","chapters":43,"synonyms":["A Baby’s Nest"],"isAdult":true,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","meanScore":64,"description":"A single father raising twins wants nothing but the best for them, but he didn't expect that he'd need breast milk! A beautiful married woman offers to sell them, and things start to get real steamy...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOPTOON+, edited)","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"title":{"english":"Breastfeeding","native":"젖동냥","romaji":"Jeotdongnyang","userPreferred":"Jeotdongnyang"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e4aebb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx136052-CKmu3CS8grpR.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx136052-CKmu3CS8grpR.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx136052-CKmu3CS8grpR.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":15,"month":12,"year":2019},"endDate":{"day":30,"month":8,"year":2020}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:39:30.213673+03:00"},"140475":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/140475-FgBKTTJY7Ry6.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx140475-QEGtrmdvbpOv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx140475-QEGtrmdvbpOv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx140475-QEGtrmdvbpOv.jpg"},"description":"This story takes place in a particular town with two infamous schools in constant dispute: Chidori High, a boys' school predominantly attended by low-class students with damning grades, and its neighbor Kikyo Girls' High, with most of its female students coming from wealthy and prestigious families. One day, high school second-year Rintaro Tsumugi, a fierce-looking but gentle-minded student at Chidori, is helping at his family's patisserie when he encounters a female customer by the name of Kaoruko Waguri. Rintaro enjoys his time with Kaoruko, as she doesn't judge him for his appearance, but this blissful peace is quickly disturbed when Rintaro makes the discovery that Kaoruko is actually a student at Kikyo. This revelation marks the beginning of the two's strenuous tale, as they fight against the limitations placed upon them by their schools and surroundings in an attempt to find their own path!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: K Manga)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":140475,"idMal":144267,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":87,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/140475","startDate":{"day":21,"month":10,"year":2021},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["薰香花朵凛然綻放","Kaoruhana","La Nobleza de las Flores","Kaoru und Rin: So nah und doch so fern","Kaoru i Rin. Rozkwitając z tobą","Bloom","The Fragrant Flower Blooms With Dignity - Kaoru \u0026 Rin","A Nobreza das Flores","Güzel Kokulu Çiçekler Zarafetle Açar","향기로운 꽃은 늠름하게 핀다"],"title":{"english":"The Fragrant Flower Blooms With Dignity","native":"薫る花は凛と咲く","romaji":"Kaoru Hana wa Rin to Saku","userPreferred":"Kaoru Hana wa Rin to Saku"},"type":"MANGA"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T18:07:35.679283+03:00"},"149332":{"value":{"Media":{"id":149332,"idMal":146949,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/149332","status":"HIATUS","type":"MANGA","format":"MANGA","synonyms":["The Youngest Son of a Master Swordsman   ","Swordmaster's Youngest Son","Youngest Son of the Renowned Swordsmanship Clan","剣術名家の末息子","劍術名家的小兒子","剑术名门的小儿子"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","meanScore":79,"description":"Jin Runcandel was destined to become the head of his swordmaster clan. But despite his best efforts, he's banished for his shoddy swordsmanship. Though Jin eventually makes a contract with the god Solderet and is freed from the curse that hindered his abilities, he meets a rather unfortunate end. In the next moment, however, he awakens as a baby, long before his tragedy began. Armed with a second chance and some new powers, Jin swears to fulfill his destiny and become the ultimate swordmaster. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"title":{"english":"The Swordmaster's Son","native":"검술명가 막내아들","romaji":"Geomsulmyeongga Mangnaeadeul","userPreferred":"Geomsulmyeongga Mangnaeadeul"},"coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx149332-adkSyOFY3c5U.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx149332-adkSyOFY3c5U.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx149332-adkSyOFY3c5U.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":30,"month":4,"year":2022},"endDate":{}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T07:10:13.556059+03:00"},"170400":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/170400-EgLAQtqhdQAx.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx170400-yMIuOIboWuoO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx170400-yMIuOIboWuoO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx170400-yMIuOIboWuoO.jpg"},"description":"The so-called “Lighthouse of the North,” the prosperous trading town of Schoarra, hides a dark underbelly: seedy slums ruled by five ruthless crime bosses. When streetwise orphan Vlad finds the brothel he works for decimated by a disgraced knight, he turns to the path of the blade, pledging himself to the pursuit of power by sword. Blessed with the ability to seek wisdom from his sentient sword, Vlad embarks upon a journey of growth and peril as swordsman in service to the powerful House Vayezid.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":170400,"idMal":163116,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/170400","startDate":{"day":19,"month":9,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Star-Embracing Swordmaster","ยอดนักดาบผู้โอบอุ้มดารา","星剑大师","星耀劍士"],"title":{"english":"The Stellar Swordmaster","native":"별을 품은 소드마스터","romaji":"Byeoreul Pumeun Swordmaster","userPreferred":"Byeoreul Pumeun Swordmaster"},"type":"MANGA"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T19:40:30.970234+03:00"},"180890":{"value":{"Media":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx180890-GRVR4m4ImzQN.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx180890-GRVR4m4ImzQN.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx180890-GRVR4m4ImzQN.jpg"},"description":"Yang-Cheon Ku, born to the virtuous House of Ku of Sanseo, the Little Star and next Head of House. Status: The world’s most hated demonic martial artist. Cause of death: Defeated during the Virtuous-Demonic War, tortured upon capture. Or so he thought. Moments after dying in the arms of his childhood friend, the Heavenly Sword herself, Seol-ah Wi, he finds himself back in the past. Already things have changed, but is it enough to ensure his second chance at life doesn’t end with the same regrets?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":180890,"idMal":172844,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/180890","startDate":{"day":4,"month":8,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Childhood Friend of the Zenith","The Best Childhood Friend in the World","天下第一的青梅竹马","天下第一人の幼馴染","L'Épée de la Seconde Chance"],"title":{"english":"Shadow of the Supreme","native":"천하제일인의 소꿉친구","romaji":"Cheonhajeirinui Sokkupchingu","userPreferred":"Cheonhajeirinui Sokkupchingu"},"type":"MANGA"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T18:08:32.895132+03:00"},"180891":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/180891-q5sLZRnEzqih.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5daee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx180891-ZBbyOWSYI41R.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx180891-ZBbyOWSYI41R.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx180891-ZBbyOWSYI41R.jpg"},"description":"The past has changed, but like a fiery comet, he still comes. Mugi Hwa, the one without equal, slashed through Murim's skies with his sword, toppling every lord who dared to face him–even Cheonma, Mugeuk Geom’s father. But Mugeuk didn’t accept defeat. Instead, he turned to the forbidden: a time-bending ritual that hurled him into his own past. Now, retracing his steps, he races against the clock until Mugi emerges once again. But this time, it's not just about power, but mending old wounds and forging new bonds to unite his people and prepare for the bloodtide to come.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Fantasy"],"id":180891,"idMal":172750,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/180891","startDate":{"day":29,"month":7,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["絕對回歸","绝对回归","ย้อนชะตาล่าข้ามภพ"],"title":{"english":"Absolute Regression","native":"절대회귀","romaji":"Jeoldaehoegwi","userPreferred":"Jeoldaehoegwi"},"type":"MANGA"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:44:13.649207+03:00"},"187427":{"value":{"Media":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#3543e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx187427-7A225QIPaIU3.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx187427-7A225QIPaIU3.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx187427-7A225QIPaIU3.png"},"description":"Fresh out of a breakup, game developer Woo-Jin has little going for him. So when he hears that the middle boss of their game is based on him, he can't resist adding a few traits to make his virtual alter ego a tad more noble. Little did he know, he would soon end up trapped in said villain's skin! With a 1 in 1,000 chance of survival, Woo-Jin now has to navigate the countless variables leading him to his impending doom. Will the tweaks he made to the character tip the scales in his favor?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy"],"id":187427,"idMal":179465,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/187427","startDate":{"day":28,"month":2,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Villain Wants to Live","A Villain's Will to Survive"],"title":{"english":"The Villain's Survival Route","native":"악당은 살고 싶다","romaji":"Akdangeun Salgo Sipda","userPreferred":"Akdangeun Salgo Sipda"},"type":"MANGA"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:47:35.641232+03:00"},"199351":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/199351-eIgIl9umb5Bw.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"CN","coverImage":{"color":"#e40d43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx199351-8cuwA3UOCXeL.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx199351-8cuwA3UOCXeL.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx199351-8cuwA3UOCXeL.jpg"},"description":"A masochistic seme who embraces his true nature × a sadistic uke who suppresses his inner self.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nTwo individuals, one indifferent to life and the other fearless of death, both possessing unique physical conditions and psychological abnormalities, cross paths in a special unit under the criminal division of the prosecution agency: the Door Hound Unit.","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Thriller"],"id":199351,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/199351","startDate":{"day":26,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Mad Dog Found Out I'm His Own Kind","Mad Dog, Same Kind"],"title":{"native":"被疯狗发现我竟是同类","romaji":"Bei Feng Gou Faxian Wo Jing Shi Tonglei","userPreferred":"Bei Feng Gou Faxian Wo Jing Shi Tonglei"},"type":"MANGA"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T19:15:02.338208+03:00"},"84505":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/84505-WT87aqSovQMA.jpg","chapters":12,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d65d1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx84505-U8vVWRmhur1Y.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx84505-U8vVWRmhur1Y.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx84505-U8vVWRmhur1Y.jpg"},"description":"A guy by the name of Kuroda-sensei is given a job as the new coach/adviser of the girls lacrosse club in an all female school called Felinus Academy for Girls but... it turns out to be a bumpy ride as he encounters sex fiends among the squad, and his adventures begins as he attempts to gain their respect as adviser.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n1-6. \u003cb\u003eChapter #1 - #6\u003c/b\u003e (第1話 - 第6話); Comic X-Eros #01, #02, #06, #08, #10, #12\u003cbr\u003e\n* 7. \u003cb\u003e2nd Season!?\u003c/b\u003e (2nd Season!?); Wanimagazine Comics Special \"Anekomori\" kakioroshi\u003cbr\u003e\n* 8. \u003cb\u003eOmake Manga Kumiko-hen\u003c/b\u003e (おまけ漫画久美子編); Joshi Luck! Toranoana Kounyuu Tokuten Shousasshi\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eBangai-hen\u003c/b\u003e (番外編); Comic X-Eros #13\u003cbr\u003e\n* 10. \u003cb\u003eAkagi Aya Massage-hen\u003c/b\u003e (赤城綾 マッサージ編); Comic Kairakuten 2014-05\u003cbr\u003e\n* 11-12. \u003cb\u003eAfter School\u003c/b\u003e (After School); Comic X-Eros #19, #21\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: (*) Chapters included in the new edition published on 2018/11/24.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":5,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai","Romance","Sports"],"id":84505,"idMal":54505,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/84505","startDate":{"day":26,"month":11,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Jyoshi Luck!","Joshi Lac!","Girls Lacrosse Club"],"title":{"native":"じょしラク！","romaji":"Joshi Luck!","userPreferred":"Joshi Luck!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:06:45.348983+03:00"}}
